  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示Branch1作为主分支，从它分出Branch2，然后两边各自提交，最后Branch2两次合并Branch1的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Branch1",
        "Branch2",
        "commit",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Branch1是mainBranchName。那分支顺序上，Branch2的order设为1可以吗？还有，初始提交id用\"a\"，然后切到Branch2提交\"f\"和\"g\"，这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Branch1",
        "Branch2",
        "order: 1",
        "commit id:\"a\"",
        "commit id:\"f\"",
        "commit id:\"g\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Branch2 order设为1。然后切回Branch1提交\"b\"，接着Branch2要第一次合并Branch1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout Branch1",
        "commit id:\"b\"",
        "checkout Branch2",
        "merge Branch1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一次合并画好了。现在Branch1继续提交\"c\"，然后Branch2再合并一次Branch1，是这个流程吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit id:\"c\"",
        "checkout Branch2",
        "merge Branch1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，两次merge Branch1。还有，配置里要把showBranches和showCommitLabel都打开，方便看清分支结构和提交标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBranches: true",
        "showCommitLabel: true"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "配置已加上。图基本完成了，您检查一下：Branch1有a、b、c三个提交，Branch2从a后分出，有f、g，然后两次合并Branch1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Branch1",
        "Branch2",
        "commit id:\"a\"",
        "commit id:\"b\"",
        "commit id:\"c\"",
        "commit id:\"f\"",
        "commit id:\"g\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，第一次合并后Branch1的\"c\"提交应该在第一次merge之后，这个顺序是对的。但确认一下，第二次merge是Branch2合并Branch1最新的c提交，不是合并b吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge Branch1",
        "commit id:\"c\""
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误，第二次merge时Branch1已经走到c提交了，所以Branch2合并的是包含c的最新状态。图结构正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout Branch1",
        "commit id:\"c\"",
        "checkout Branch2",
        "merge Branch1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
